<h1>Scoring</h1>
<li><h3><i>Shoot On Sight</h3></i></li>
<table border="1"><tr><td>
<p>Players stand just outside the 21m line with another player standing opposite them on the 45m line with a sliotar each.</p>
<p>One player stands in goals as goalkeeper.</p>
<p>On the whistle each player takes it in turn to play the sliotar into the inside player who then attempts to turn and score</p>
</table></tr></td>
<br>